data.description: Looking for a spacious and comfortable single family home with acreage? Look no further! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is the perfect property for those looking for ample space with a country feel. With 1936 square feet of living space, this property boasts plenty of room for relaxing, entertaining, and enjoying your daily life.    Inside, you'll be greeted by a range of features and finishes. The home's stainless steel appliances are just the beginning - you'll also love the flex space with built-in cabinetry, perfect for storage or as a home office. In addition, you'll find tile flooring throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, and wood laminate throughout the living spaces, providing a warm and welcoming ambiance.  And there is plenty of opportunity to put your own personality and touch into the home to make it your dream oasis.    The home's 3 bedrooms are generously sized, each offering ample closet space and plenty of natural light. The 2 bathrooms are equally well-appointed, with finishes that add to the home's overall feel.    But perhaps the best feature of this home is the large back porch and acreage. This large outdoor space is perfect for entertaining, gardening, or simply relaxing in the sunshine. With plenty of room for outdoor furniture, barbecues, and more, this backyard is sure to become your family's favorite spot to spend time together. And for those of you loving the idea of farm life, but not wanting to commit to large amounts of acreage, the property is already set up with a livestock round pen and chicken coop.  Imagine the possibilities!     Don't miss your chance to own your part of country living. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
